claim: Flublok is approved for adults 18 years and older
explanation: The image is a table comparing the rates of local and systemic adverse events for Flublok (N=972) versus IIV3 (N=967), listing percentages of pain, redness, headache, fatigue, etc. It does not mention the ages of the study participants nor any approval status or age indication.
